text: Coral Shores High School is a senior high school in Islamorada, Florida, \- Mapping the address shows it is in Islamorada town, not Tavernier CDP. Compare with the Islamorada map. 2010 U.S. Census Bureau map for Tavernier and pages 1, 2, and 3. near Tavernier. It is within the Monroe County School District. ==History== 1952 was its year of establishment. it had fewer than 800 students.
